wmsLayer.title: GA0308 Cloates 3m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of the survey area off Point Cloates from marine survey GA0308, collected on the Carnarvon Shelf, Western Australia. A total of six areas were surveyed and gridded at three metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 10-120 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/72005.
